author: rickhall
msg: Very rough implementation of resolver algorithm for require-bundle. This
implementation is not complete, but it works on many different examples.
Currently, only the resolving portion has been worked on, the wires that
are created as a result of a require-bundle are not valid. Also, the resolver
currently assumes that all required packages are exported and it only works
for bundles that have not yet been resolved.
